data.description: Amazing space in the iconic Riverbend neighborhood! Master on main with incredible closet space and newly remodeled master bath. There are 3 additional bedrooms and an office or bonus room upstairs. One bedroom on second floor has on-suite bathroom with two large walk in closets. Kitchen has freshly updated cabinets, granite countertops, and opens to living room with fireplace. Climate controlled sunroom off the living room that leads to custom deck. Laundry and pantry on main floor as well as a half bath. Downstairs has the 2nd fireplace, half bath, and great bar area with sink and lots of storage. Double car garage that currently holds sizeable bass boat. Extra closets and storage space on every level. Great level backyard with privacy!**May be possibility of buyer assuming FHA loan based on terms, conditions, and eligibility.
